Current Approaches On Technical Sciences
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=7172860&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2018-10-11
 12,19
“Current Approaches on Technical Sciences” is a research book that has been received by expert authors in the field of book. This book important contributions to academicians, students and practitioners, and also the literature. “Current Approaches on Technical Sciences” contains that “Modification Study of Canola Oil under the Catalysis of Cinko Oxide” written by Zehra Gülten YALÇIN, M. Bora AKIN, Mustafa DAĞ, Ercan AYDOĞMUŞ & Ali ÖZ, “A Non-Linear Model Proposal for Multiple Response Optimization Usıng Desirability Function Approach” written by Ali İhsan BOYACI & Ramazan EVREN, “Distribution of Tobacco Products with Integer Linear Programming” written by Altay Uğur GUL, Funda GENCLER & Berna TURKEKUL, “Determination of Forest Fire Monitoring Points Using 0-1 Integer Programming” written by Altay Uğur GUL, Funda GENCLER & Berna TURKEKUL
